  "detailed_description": "If you like incremental/clicker games this game is for you<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1641330/extras/1bcc7b8a66230e677caafd1e7ce544d9.poster.avif?t=1625944070\" width=232 height=274 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1641330/extras/1bcc7b8a66230e677caafd1e7ce544d9.webm?t=1625944070\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1641330/extras/1bcc7b8a66230e677caafd1e7ce544d9.mp4?t=1625944070\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Tree Strike Features A Small Yet Compelling Loop</h2><br><strong>Hit Trees to Get Fruit Wood and Lots Of Money</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1641330/extras/a55cb87d3e347ae754409ea6fa94eb65.poster.avif?t=1625944070\" width=232 height=282 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1641330/extras/a55cb87d3e347ae754409ea6fa94eb65.webm?t=1625944070\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1641330/extras/a55cb87d3e347ae754409ea6fa94eb65.mp4?t=1625944070\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Die!</strong><br>Dying is bound to happen in tree strike so don’t mind it<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1641330/extras/d4c05f49e5b436be36f8282794c964e6.poster.avif?t=1625944070\" width=232 height=166 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1641330/extras/d4c05f49e5b436be36f8282794c964e6.webm?t=1625944070\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1641330/extras/d4c05f49e5b436be36f8282794c964e6.mp4?t=1625944070\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><strong>Powerup!</strong><br>Each time you die you come back stronger a lot of incremental and movement upgrades to choose from<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1641330/extras/2c4bef1e57b240900a398f8da356de8c.poster.avif?t=1625944070\" width=300 height=410 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1641330/extras/2c4bef1e57b240900a398f8da356de8c.webm?t=1625944070\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1641330/extras/2c4bef1e57b240900a398f8da356de8c.mp4?t=1625944070\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><br><strong>Also Co-Op!</strong><br>You can see numbers go up with a friend too!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1641330/extras/1500981bd65058a92f64b62badb345fe.poster.avif?t=1625944070\" width=484 height=198 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1641330/extras/1500981bd65058a92f64b62badb345fe.webm?t=1625944070\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1641330/extras/1500981bd65058a92f64b62badb345fe.mp4?t=1625944070\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br>Key features<br><br>-An infinite ammount of upgrades to get<br>-5 Zones to see and UPGRADE<br>-65 Achievements to get<br>-Local coop<br>-Chill OST<br>-Crunchy VFX",
